Package: axon
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: streaming security evidence normalization and export CLI
 Axon ingests scanner output, normalizes findings into a canonical model,
 deduplicates and correlates related evidence, and exports the result as JSON,
 SARIF, or AWS ASFF.
 .
 The current architecture uses a two-pass ingest pipeline with offset-based
 hydration so large reports can be processed without retaining every finding in
 memory during export.
